Order Service (8081) → order-created-topic
      ↓
Inventory Service (8082) → inventory-reserved-topic / inventory-failed-topic
      ↓
Payment Service (8083) → payment-success-topic / payment-failed-topic
      ↓
Notification Service (8084) → prints notification
