NOTIFICATION SERVICE (Kafka Consumer/Producer)
==========================================
Required dependencies
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.kafka</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-kafka</artifactId>
</dependency>

<dependency>
    <groupId>org.projectlombok</groupId>
    <artifactId>lombok</artifactId>
    <optional>true</optional>
</dependency>

<!-- If email/SMS is added -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-mail</artifactId>
</dependency>
Here No spring-boot-starter-web will add , Because it does not expose REST APIs.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Responsibility:-
Consume Payment events:
payment-success-topic → notify user
payment-failed-topic → notify user
No producer needed
Only logging or sending notification (console/email for simplicity)